<p>四、根据你的需要自己设置相关的有效性，如下图所示：</p>

<p><a href="https://gss0.baidu.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/5882b2b7d0a20cf4b4a5233672094b36acaf9926.jpg" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="点击查看大图"><img src="https://gss0.baidu.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/wh%3D600%2C800/sign=b6f26a52a21ea8d38a777c02a73a1c76/5882b2b7d0a20cf4b4a5233672094b36acaf9926.jpg" /></a></p>

